short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes links at random into rickrolls and other fun and annoying memes! Annoy yourself or your friends!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:

⭐⭐⭐SPECIAL FEATURES:⭐⭐⭐
